14#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_EUI48_108_C
15#define RDATA_GENERIC_EUI48_108_C
16
17#include <string.h>
18
19#define RRTYPE_EUI48_ATTRIBUTES (0)
20
21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_eui48(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24 unsigned char eui48[6];
25 unsigned int l0, l1, l2, l3, l4, l5;
26 int n;
27
28 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_eui48);
29
30 UNUSED(type);
31 UNUSED(rdclass);
32 UNUSED(origin);
33 UNUSED(options);
34 UNUSED(callbacks);
35
36 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
37 false));
38 n = sscanf(DNS_AS_STR(token), "%2x-%2x-%2x-%2x-%2x-%2x",
39 &l0, &l1, &l2, &l3, &l4, &l5);
40 if (n != 6 || l0 > 255U || l1 > 255U || l2 > 255U || l3 > 255U ||
41 l4 > 255U || l5 > 255U)
42 return (DNS_R_BADEUI);
43
44 eui48[0] = l0;
45 eui48[1] = l1;
46 eui48[2] = l2;
47 eui48[3] = l3;
48 eui48[4] = l4;
49 eui48[5] = l5;
50 return (mem_tobuffer(target, eui48, sizeof(eui48)));
51}
52
53static inline isc_result_t
54totext_eui48(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
55 char buf[sizeof("xx-xx-xx-xx-xx-xx")];
56
57 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_eui48);
58 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 6);
59
60 UNUSED(tctx);
61
62 (void)snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%02x-%02x-%02x-%02x-%02x-%02x",
63 rdata->data[0], rdata->data[1], rdata->data[2],
64 rdata->data[3], rdata->data[4], rdata->data[5]);
65 return (str_totext(buf, target));
66}
67
68static inline isc_result_t
69fromwire_eui48(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
70 isc_region_t sregion;
71
72 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_eui48);
73
74 UNUSED(type);
75 UNUSED(options);
76 UNUSED(rdclass);
77 UNUSED(dctx);
78
79 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sregion);
80 if (sregion.length != 6)
81 return (DNS_R_FORMERR);
82 isc_buffer_forward(source, sregion.length);
83 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sregion.base, sregion.length));
84}
85
86static inline isc_result_t
87towire_eui48(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
88
89 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_eui48);
90 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 6);
91
92 UNUSED(cctx);
93
94 return (mem_tobuffer(target, rdata->data, rdata->length));
95}
96
97static inline int
98compare_eui48(ARGS_COMPARE) {
99 isc_region_t region1;
100 isc_region_t region2;
101
102 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
103 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
104 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_eui48);
105 REQUIRE(rdata1->length == 6);
106 REQUIRE(rdata2->length == 6);
107
108 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
109 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
110 return (isc_region_compare(&region1, &region2));
111}
112
113static inline isc_result_t
114fromstruct_eui48(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
115 dns_rdata_eui48_t *eui48 = source;
116
117 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_eui48);
118 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
119 REQUIRE(eui48->common.rdtype == type);
120 REQUIRE(eui48->common.rdclass == rdclass);
121
122 UNUSED(type);
123 UNUSED(rdclass);
124
125 return (mem_tobuffer(target, eui48->eui48, sizeof(eui48->eui48)));
126}
127
128static inline isc_result_t
129tostruct_eui48(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
130 dns_rdata_eui48_t *eui48 = target;
131
132 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_eui48);
133 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
134 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 6);
135
136 UNUSED(mctx);
137
138 eui48->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
139 eui48->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
140 ISC_LINK_INIT(&eui48->common, link);
141
142 memmove(eui48->eui48, rdata->data, rdata->length);
143 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
144}
145
146static inline void
147freestruct_eui48(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
148 dns_rdata_eui48_t *eui48 = source;
149
150 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
151 REQUIRE(eui48->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_eui48);
152
153 return;
154}
155
156static inline isc_result_t
157additionaldata_eui48(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
158
159 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_eui48);
160 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 6);
161
162 UNUSED(rdata);
163 UNUSED(add);
164 UNUSED(arg);
165
166 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
167}
168
169static inline isc_result_t
170digest_eui48(ARGS_DIGEST) {
171 isc_region_t r;
172
173 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_eui48);
174 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 6);
175
176 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
177
178 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
179}

182checkowner_eui48(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
183
184 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_eui48);
185
186 UNUSED(name);
187 UNUSED(type);
188 UNUSED(rdclass);
189 UNUSED(wildcard);
190

194static inline bool
195checknames_eui48(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
196

198 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 6);
199
200 UNUSED(rdata);
201 UNUSED(owner);
202 UNUSED(bad);
203
204 return (true);

207static inline int
208casecompare_eui48(ARGS_COMPARE) {
209 return (compare_eui48(rdata1, rdata2));
210}
